Hi Ken,

I don't have account so click "Create an account" link which takes me to:
     http://eplex.cs.ucf.edu/user/registration
I fill in the form under user registration (all fields are required)
and click the 'Register' button which attempts to take me to:
     http://eplex.cs.ucf.edu/user/registration.register
which reports '404 Not Found'.

If it was my HTML, I'd probably be looking at full stop before register :-)

Hope this helps.

Rob Marsden
